  "narrative": {
    "intro": "NAICS 541618 (Other Management Consulting Services) has $115M in contract obligations in FY2026 to date, with 477 awards and an average award size of $240K. Obligations are down 86.4% year over year. Annual obligations have varied across recent fiscal years: FY21 totaled $537M, FY22 totaled $913M, FY23 totaled $864M, FY24 totaled $1.3B, and FY25 totaled $843M. The FY2026 to date total of $115M represents a sharp decline relative to prior full-year totals. Top buying agencies so far this year include the Department of Defense with $45.8M and the Department of Health and Human Services with $28.8M. The largest vendors in FY2026 to date are ISLAND PEER REVIEW ORGANIZATION INC with $52.4M and PALANTIR USG INC with $22M. This profile reflects current fiscal-year-to-date obligations and a concentrated set of buyers and vendors through the partial FY2026 reporting period.",
